{"tid":228430,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"梁美芬老母被車撞飛入院","createTime":"2017-05-04T00:59:23.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-04T09:08:41.000Z","uid":51271,"like":486,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"f8e34548ca1ecb71cbf7e4b93086e485831f162d","tid":228430,"uid":51271,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-04T00:59:23.000Z","msg":"但死唔去<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.mingpao.com/pns/dailynews/web_tc/article/20170504/s00002/1493834670348\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fpns%2Fdailynews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20170504%2Fs00002%2F1493834670348&d=28xXuG3%2BZgR4L17YEenOItU7RO4jIL0fLOArxO5LqtQ%3D&h=58f44d1f\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fpns%2Fdailynews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20170504%2Fs00002%2F1493834670348&h=716ea270\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.mingpao.com/pns/dailynews/web_tc/article/20170504/s00002/1493834670348</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://fs.mingpao.com/pns/20170504/s00046/1ad8f926940b2404591d871ab7014441.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Fpns%2F20170504%2Fs00046%2F1ad8f926940b2404591d871ab7014441.jpg&h=64dffdad&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n【明報專訊】經民聯梁美芬呢個五一及佛誕假期都好忙，話有唔少地區活動及會議要參加，但噚日百忙中都抽時間同86歲嘅媽媽飲茶，因為媽媽啱啱傷癒出院。梁美芬同Emily講，佢媽媽上周去沙田一個商場酒樓飲茶，其間喺商場內被人用載滿貨嘅木頭推車撞倒，頭部腫晒，好彩係外傷，無傷及臉部。<br />\n<br />\n梁美芬：商場應檢討<br />\n<br />\n梁美芬話，媽媽講當時好險，佢從後面被撞倒飛前倒地。梁美芬認為商場真係要檢討一下，唔應該畀人喺場內再係咁，用疊得太高貨物嘅木頭車喺商場送貨，因為會危及途人。可幸嘅係梁媽媽已無大礙，所以佢兩母女都話好感恩。"},{"pid":"d11137c70b06108c7d6ee25b31b330ce7a08e453","tid":228430,"uid":17641,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-04T00:59:52.000Z","msg":"R.i.p<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9257795191c9b26a40dbbad3b1c4ec993ab31717","tid":228430,"uid":50595,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-04T01:00:44.000Z","msg":"手推車<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pi